SELECT 'ChangeDeliveryLine' || '::' || "DeliveryLine_Changes"."ID"  AS "ID",
       "DeliveryLine"."ID"                                          AS "DeliveryLine",
       "DeliveryLine_Changes"."Time"                                AS "Time",
       "DeliveryLine_Changes"."ChangedBy"                           AS "ExecutedBy",
       "DeliveryLine_Changes"."Attribute"                           AS "ChangedAttribute",
       "DeliveryLine_Changes"."ExecutionType"                       AS "ExecutionType",
       "DeliveryLine_Changes"."OldValue"                            AS "OldValue",
       "DeliveryLine_Changes"."NewValue"                            AS "NewValue"
FROM "o_custom_DeliveryLine" AS "DeliveryLine"
    LEFT JOIN "c_o_custom_DeliveryLine" AS "DeliveryLine_Changes"
        ON "DeliveryLine"."ID" = "DeliveryLine_Changes"."ObjectID"
            AND "DeliveryLine_Changes"."Attribute" IN (
                'WeightUnit',
                'Quantity',
                'StorageLocation',
                'MaterialGroup',
                'NetWeight',
                'VolumeUnit',
                'Volume',
                'Plant'
            )
WHERE "DeliveryLine_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL
